SC-MONOME
----------------------------------------------------------------------
SuperCollider classes to simplify interfacing with Monome controllers
via SerialOSC.

Monome.sc:
 - represents a single Monome controller.
   Call .led(x,y,s), .ledRow(y, xOffset, i), .ledCol(x, yOffset, i) 
   to set lights.
   
   Set .action to respond to button-press events.

MonomEm.sc
 - a simple graphical monome emulator, for testing when your
   controller is not around.

